item.title: My Week in Music #1: 2018/10/05 - 2018/10/12
item.description: Last.fm is a website that can keep track of users and their listening habits. I’ve been listening to music with Last.fm since 2010 and am slightly obsessive over my music stats. These stats are for my listening from the past week. My week for October 5, 2018 to October 12, 2018 Top 10 Artists Top 10 Artists It’s no surprise that Coheed and Cambria has been pretty much all that I’ve been listening to.
